, certainly earlier in my career, was questioned.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that mental toughness\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud of that side of things.\\\"\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that side\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some questioned the wisdom of Murray carrying on to a fifth Games when Wimbledon in early summer had laid on such a fitting faux farewell, following his first-round doubles defeat alongside brother Jamie.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0181530905567686e-37, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wisdom\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth Games\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"early summer\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"such a fitting faux farewell\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"his first-round doubles defeat\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"brother Jamie\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At a set and a break down on Sunday night, it looked a fool's errand.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday night\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"a fool's